<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Interaction | Next-gen Tech Edu</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/awesome-lists/2.frontend/1.web/widgets/interaction/</link><atom:link href="https://ng-tech.icu/books/awesome-lists/2.frontend/1.web/widgets/interaction/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><description>Interaction</description><generator>Wowchemy (https://wowchemy.com)</generator><language>zh</language><image><url>https://ng-tech.icu/media/sharing.png</url><title>Interaction</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/awesome-lists/2.frontend/1.web/widgets/interaction/</link></image><item><title>Drag &amp; Resize</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/awesome-lists/2.frontend/1.web/widgets/interaction/drag-resize/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/awesome-lists/2.frontend/1.web/widgets/interaction/drag-resize/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="drag--drop">Drag &amp;amp; Drop&lt;/h1>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/bevacqua/dragula" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2014-dragula
&lt;img src="https://ng-tech.icu/assets/code.svg" style="max-width: 100px;display: inline-flex;"/>&lt;/a>: Drag and drop so simple it hurts&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/taye/interact.js" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2016-interact.js
&lt;img src="https://ng-tech.icu/assets/code.svg" style="max-width: 100px;display: inline-flex;"/>&lt;/a>: JavaScript drag and drop, resizing and multi-touch gestures with inertia and snapping for modern browsers (and also IE8+)&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/SortableJS/Vue.Draggable" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2016-Vue.Draggable
&lt;img src="https://ng-tech.icu/assets/code.svg" style="max-width: 100px;display: inline-flex;"/>&lt;/a>: Vue drag-and-drop component based on Sortable.js.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/Shopify/draggable" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2017-draggable
&lt;img src="https://ng-tech.icu/assets/code.svg" style="max-width: 100px;display: inline-flex;"/>&lt;/a>: The JavaScript Drag &amp;amp; Drop library your grandparents warned you about. Draggable comes with additional modules: Sortable, Droppable, Swappable. Draggable itself does not perform any sorting behaviour while dragging, but does the heavy lifting;&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/atlassian/react-beautiful-dnd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2017-react-beautiful-dnd
&lt;img src="https://ng-tech.icu/assets/code.svg" style="max-width: 100px;display: inline-flex;"/>&lt;/a>: Beautiful and accessible drag and drop for lists with React.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/react-dnd/react-dnd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2017-React DnD
&lt;img src="https://ng-tech.icu/assets/code.svg" style="max-width: 100px;display: inline-flex;"/>&lt;/a>: Drag and Drop for React.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>Scroll</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/awesome-lists/2.frontend/1.web/widgets/interaction/scroll/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/awesome-lists/2.frontend/1.web/widgets/interaction/scroll/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="web-interaction-widgets-list">Web Interaction Widgets List&lt;/h1>
